These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-1::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, chaman, montecristo, tiparillo
House: victorian, wooden, cottage, farmhouse
4 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, dog, frog
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, ship, tram, van
 1. the wooden house is on the left or right of the person driving the ship##3
 2. the chaman-smoker is the farmhouse house##1
 3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person driving the tram is on the right of the chaman-smoker##1
 5. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the cottage house is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
 7. the montecristo-smoker is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1
 8. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the cottage house##1
 9. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left##1
10. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
11. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the ritmeester-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |      3      |   4   |
| Cigar    | montecristo   | chaman       | ritmeester | tiparillo   |
| House        | wooden    | farmhouse  | cottage      | victorian |
| Pet         | frog      | chinchilla | dog         | cat   |
| Transport   | quad-bike | ship       | tram        | van   |

