.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-3::.
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, grapefruit, peach, potato
City: miami, colone, paris, nizza
House: farmhouse, gothic-revival, modern, palace
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, cycling, ice-hockey, volleyball
 1. the person traveling to paris is the person eating peach##1
 2. the person traveling to miami is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the person eating potato is on the left or right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##3
 4. the modern house is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
 5. the palace house is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1
 6. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left or right of the person who's sport is volleyball##3
 7. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 8. the farmhouse house is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person traveling to colone##2
 9. the person eating potato is on the left of the person eating cauliflower##1
10. the person eating grapefruit is on the left or right of the person eating potato##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |     4      |
| Food          | grapefruit | potato  | cauliflower | peach      |
| City   | miami       | nizza    | colone      | paris      |
| House           | palace     | farmhouse     | gothic-revival         | modern   |
| Sport         | ice-hockey | cricket | cycling     | volleyball |

