2. the australian is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
3. the photographer is the prince-smoker##1
4. the siglo-smoker is on the far left##1
5. the french is the prince-smoker##1
6. the canadian is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person who likes blue is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1
8. the videographer is between the person who likes coral and the polish##2
9. the librarian is on the left or right of the person who likes yellow##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |      4       |
| Job           | lawyer     | videographer | librarian | photographer |
| Cigar   | siglo     | bolivar       | tiparillo      | prince   |
| Nationality   | canadian   | australian   | polish    | french       |
| Color           | coral | aquamarine        | blue    | yellow        |

