.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-5::.
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, bird, pony, rat
There 4 different types of food: carrot, kiwi, pineapple, zucchini
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, metal, reggae, trance
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, baccarat, swisher, old-henry
 1. the alhambra-smoker is on the left or right of the person eating kiwi##3
 2. the person eating zucchini is on the left or right of the person eating carrot##3
 3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1
 4. the person eating zucchini is on the right of the person eating carrot##1
 5. the owner of the rat is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1
 6. the owner of the rat is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the fan of funk is on the left or right of the person eating zucchini##3
 8. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person eating kiwi##1
 9. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
10. the fan of trance is between the owner of the guinea-pig and the fan of reggae##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |     3     |     4      |
| Pet      | rat | guinea-pig | pony     | bird       |
| Food          | carrot   | zucchini    | pineapple | kiwi       |
| Music-Genre   | funk     | metal       | trance    | reggae     |
| Cigar         | swisher  | old-henry  | alhambra | baccarat |

