The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, soul, country, pop
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, parkour, biathlon, cricket
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, snowmobile, train, trike
 1. the fan of metal is on the left of the person driving the train##1
 2. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3
 3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the fan of metal##3
 4. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far right##1
 5. the person driving the trike is between the fan of pop and the fan of country##2
 6. the fan of metal is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 7. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3
 8. the person who's sport is cricket is the person driving the snowmobile##1
 9. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left or right of the fan of pop##3
10. the person drinking fanta is on the far right##1
11. the person who's sport is parkour is the fan of pop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2    |      3      |     4      |
| Beverage    | soy-milk   | coffee | almond-milk | fanta      |
| Music-Genre        | pop | metal | country   | soul     |
| Sport         | parkour     | cycling    | biathlon       | cricket     |
| Transport   | scooter    | trike  | train       | snowmobile |

