There 4 different types of food: cranberry, papaya, kiwi, peach
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, handball, ice-hockey, surfing
 1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person who's sport is handball is on the left or right of the person watching scientific movies##3
 3. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
 4. the person eating kiwi is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the person eating peach is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
 6. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
 7. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far left##1
 8. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
 9. the person eating peach is the person driving the taxi##1
10. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person eating papaya##1
11. the person eating kiwi is the person driving the roller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |       3       |     4     |
| Transport      | taxi      | bike  | airplane | roller      |
