.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-20::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: orange, coral, chestnut, lilac
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, dancer, mechanic, scientist
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, comedy, mystery, satire
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, poker, scrabble, whist
 1. the person who likes orange is on the far right##1
 2. the person playing poker is on the right of the analyst##1
 3. the person who likes coral is on the left of the person who likes lilac##1
 4. the dancer is between the person playing scrabble and the person playing poker##2
 5. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person who likes chestnut##3
 6. the person watching adventure movies is between the dancer and the person playing mah-jongg##2
 7. the person watching mystery movies is the scientist##1
 8. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
 9. the person who likes chestnut is the dancer##1
10. the person watching adventure movies is the mechanic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3     |     4     |
| Color          | coral | lilac   | chestnut   | orange |
| Job           | analyst   | mechanic     | dancer   | scientist |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy    | adventure    | satire   | mystery   |
| Game         | mah-jongg    | poker | whist | scrabble    |

 